        <h2>Welcome to the Web Development Course!</h2>
        <p>In this course, you'll learn the fundamentals of web development and start building your own websites from scratch.</p>

        <h4>About Web Development</h4>
        <p>Web development is the process of creating websites and applications that run on the internet. It involves several key technologies including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>HTML</strong> (HyperText Markup Language) – The structure of web pages.</li>
            <li><strong>CSS</strong> (Cascading Style Sheets) – The styling of web pages.</li>
            <li><strong>JavaScript</strong> – The functionality of web pages, making them interactive and dynamic.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Whether you're building a personal blog or a complex web application, learning web development is an essential skill in today’s digital world.</p>

        <h4>Course Overview</h4>
        <p>This course is designed for beginners who want to get started with web development. Over the duration of the course, you will:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Learn HTML to create the structure of web pages.</li>
            <li>Understand CSS to design and layout web pages effectively.</li>
            <li>Master JavaScript to add interactivity and dynamic features to your websites.</li>
            <li>Complete hands-on projects to apply what you've learned in real-world scenarios.</li>
        </ul>

